Doc: Package testing provides support for automated testing of Go packages.

Name: jwt
Doc: Package jwt is a Go implementation of JSON Web Tokens: http://self-issued.info/docs/draft-jones-json-web-token.html

Name: blowfish
Doc: Package blowfish implements Bruce Schneier's Blowfish encryption algorithm.

Name: bcrypt
Doc: Package bcrypt implements Provos and Mazires's bcrypt adaptive hashing algorithm.

Name: buffer
Doc: Package buffer provides a pool-allocated byte buffer.

Name: slog
Doc: Package slog provides structured logging, in which log records include a message, a severity level, and various other attributes expressed as key-value pairs.

Name: color
Doc: Package color implements a basic color library.

Name: image
Doc: Package image implements a basic 2-D image library.

Name: lzw
Doc: Package lzw implements the Lempel-Ziv-Welch compressed data format, described in T. A. Welch, A Technique for High-Performance Data Compression, Computer, 17(6) (June 1984), pp 8-19.

Name: palette
Doc: Package palette provides standard color palettes.

Name: imageutil
Doc: Package imageutil contains code shared by image-related packages.

Name: draw
Doc: Package draw provides image composition functions.

Name: gif
Doc: Package gif implements a GIF image decoder and encoder.

Name: jpeg
Doc: Package jpeg implements a JPEG image decoder and encoder.

Name: adler32
Doc: Package adler32 implements the Adler-32 checksum.

Name: zlib
Doc: Package zlib implements reading and writing of zlib format compressed data, as specified in RFC 1950.

Name: png
Doc: Package png implements a PNG image decoder and encoder.

Name: mail
Doc: Package mail implements parsing of mail messages.

Name: smtp
Doc: Package smtp implements the Simple Mail Transfer Protocol as defined in RFC 5321.

Name: expvar
Doc: Package expvar provides a standardized interface to public variables, such as operation counters in servers.

Name: quantile
Doc: Package quantile computes approximate quantiles over an unbounded data stream within low memory and CPU bounds.

Name: xxhash
Doc: Package xxhash implements the 64-bit variant of xxHash (XXH64) as described at http://cyan4973.github.io/xxHash/.

Name: model
Doc: Package model contains common data structures that are shared across Prometheus components and libraries.

Name: metrics
Doc: Package metrics provides a stable interface to access implementation-defined metrics exported by the Go runtime.

Name: protodelim
Doc: Package protodelim marshals and unmarshals varint size-delimited messages.

Name: expfmt
Doc: Package expfmt contains tools for reading and writing Prometheus metrics.

Name: cgo
Doc: Package cgo contains runtime support for code generated by the cgo tool.

Name: prometheus
Doc: Package prometheus is the core instrumentation package.

Name: promauto
Doc: Package promauto provides alternative constructors for the fundamental Prometheus metric types and their Vec and Func variants.

Name: header
Doc: Package header provides functions for parsing HTTP headers.

Name: promhttp
Doc: Package promhttp provides tooling around HTTP servers and clients.

Name: signal
Doc: Package signal implements access to incoming signals.
